	Add --enable-werror configure option. Add -Wall and -Werror after
	all tests so they don't cause failures.
	[805eb7c4af8b] <1.7>

	* config.h.in, configure, configure.in, missing.h, sudo.h,
	sudo_noexec.c:
	Add configure test for missing errno declaration and only declare it
	ourselves if it is missing.
	[9e26d7bc28b9] <1.7>

	* alias.c:
	Include errno.h before sudo.h to avoid conflicting with the system
	definition of errno.
	[991e5efb9333] <1.7>

