	[8ed46ff3141a] <1.7>

	* sudoers.pod:
	set_home and always_set_home have an effect if HOME is present in
	the env_keep list.
	[a2b26d62176d] <1.7>

	* env.c:
	Make -H flag work when HOME is listed in env_keep. Also makes
	"set_home" and "always_set_home" override override HOME in env_keep.
	[91d842b6adc6] <1.7>

