	callback.
	[26d413ddb6dd] <1.7>

	* WHATSNEW:
	Do not call set_fqdn() until sudoers parses (where is gets run as a
	callback).
	[582453a993a1] <1.7>

	* sudo.c:
	Do not call set_fqdn() until sudoers parses (where is gets run as a
	callback). Otherwise, if sudo is built --with-fqdn the fqdn will be
	set even if !fqdn is set in sudoers.
	[aa01e867d1bb] <1.7>

