	passing a command to be run via the shell for the -s and -i options.
	[d35a3f4cb3c0] <1.7>

	* sudo.c:
	Add missing braces that broke -i mode.
	[7fe124b078ec] <1.7>

	* linux_audit.c:
	Fix linux_audit_command() return value
	[0c582476181c] <1.7>

