	* script.c:
	Sprinkle some more O_NOCTTY and call grantpt() before unlockpt()
	[d94bd5c9bf4e]

	* script.c:
	Call tcgetpgrp() in the parent, not the child and have the child
	spin until it is granted. Fixes a race on darwin.
	[6e8d435339ce]

