	* parse.lex:
	Remove us of unput() in favor of yyless() which is cheaper.
	[c61291902beb]

	* parse.yacc:
	Allow an empty sudoers file.
	[62fb111db2e7]

2004-09-28  Todd C. Miller  <Todd.Miller@courtesan.com>

	* mon_systrace.c:
