2004-05-28  Todd C. Miller  <Todd.Miller@courtesan.com>

	* tgetpass.c:
	Use SA_INTERRUPT so SunOS works correctly, avoid stdio and just use
	read/write as it is simpler.
	[30f5446ee8b0]

