	due to the fact that find_path() is called *before* sudoers is read.
	[6808df7e417c]

2004-01-30  Todd C. Miller  <Todd.Miller@courtesan.com>

	* sudo_edit.c:
	Do not require _PATH_USRTMP to be set.
	[546f3270dd10]

	* BUGS, CHANGES, TODO:
	sync
	[4205ddeab781]

	* sudo.man.in:
	regen
	[e2143690a88a]

	* sudo.pod:
