	Don't lie about making a module, it does the wrong thing on mach
	[7629b28f5688]

	* ltmain.sh:
	Remove requirement that libs must begin with "lib". They don't when
	we point directly at the lib using LD_PRELOAD or its equivalent.
	[d66f3de6ec85]

