	PAM_PROMPT_ECHO_ON Block SIGINT and SIGTSTP during auth remove a
	useless umask setting Change error from BAD_ALLOCATION ->
	BAD_AUTH_INIT (for use with sia/PAM) Some cosmetic changes to auth.c
	for consistency
